{"tid":1226472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣報 邊個話遊行示威冇用 邊個就係鬼","createTime":"2019-06-15T11:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T15:07:29.000Z","uid":12746,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"96c9c5d3e322cc82d99a7b726c14d2481e877ab2","tid":1226472,"uid":12746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:43:45.000Z","msg":"如果今次唔係因為我地出黎 政府一定會無動於衷<br />\n無論你係和理非非定係勇武派都有你既作用<br />\n冇咗勇武派 政府根本唔識驚 <br />\n冇咗和理非非 義士好快就俾人驅散同捉哂<br />\n<br />\n雖然之前民主派比人DQ 搞到冇咗否決權 但我想講 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">否決權係喺我地市民手入面</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以聽日616一定要出黎 示威可以令政府對送中卻步<br />\n要政府收返「暴動」既定性 都一定得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tvao8in.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftvao8in.png&h=ffaf26e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1ea8bf9f28aa8678eb01938abb3c120fa879b34","tid":1226472,"uid":12746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:55:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be652164405ea90c1a9d74493e94264136a92ef0","tid":1226472,"uid":12746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:03:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"430b3101696d668d16e9b60083bf355652034056","tid":1226472,"uid":12746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:06:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c2866d31736cd68d12c080442ceb5fd07c0acc7","tid":1226472,"uid":12746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:11:08.000Z","msg":"重有記者朋友呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係唔幫佢地攞反個公道啊<br />\n為咗幫我哋報道真相 食咁多催淚彈 胡椒噴霧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41e53323f0581be4bd456c5d5dd07688df868df","tid":1226472,"uid":12746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:14:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1446eebd844285c998d79539281a2dfcbafec883","tid":1226472,"uid":12746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-1